room_title: Escape room "Jigsaw" by Rooms of No Return in Bakersfield
room_description:
Jigsaw has kidnapped you and you have to go through a set of trials. He has designed each of his rooms to teach you a lesson. Your desperate effort to escape will bring out your most primitive instincts to surface. You must solve all of Jigsaw's puzzles and traps in order to make it out alive. Do you have what it takes to survive Jigsaw's trap?
CAUTION: Very interactive. Drinking Involved (non-alcoholic).
